request.description:
Socket.IO server endpoint is the default /socket.io.
Namespace: /chat

Client example:
io('{{baseUrl}}/chat', {
  auth: { token: '{{accessToken}}' }
})

Alternatively server also reads Authorization header (Bearer token) from handshake headers.

Client emit: chat:message:list
Payload (cursor based):
{ "conversationId": "<conversationId>", "cursor": "<messageId>", "limit": 30 }

Or page based:
{ "conversationId": "<conversationId>", "page": 1, "limit": 30 }

Ack data: messages[]

Client emit: chat:message:send
Payload (text):
{ "conversationId": "<conversationId>", "text": "Hello" }

Payload (attachment):
{
  "conversationId": "<conversationId>",
  "text": "optional",
  "attachment": {
    "type": "image",
    "url": "https://...",
    "name": "photo.jpg",
    "size": 12345
  }
}

Server broadcast: chat:message:new to room
